Class RandomDistributedScalarEncoder.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.numenta.nupic.encoders.Encoder.Builder<RandomDistributedScalarEncoder.Builder,RandomDistributedScalarEncoder>

  • Enclosing class:
    RandomDistributedScalarEncoder

    public static class RandomDistributedScalarEncoder.Builder
extends Encoder.Builder<RandomDistributedScalarEncoder.Builder,RandomDistributedScalarEncoder>

    Returns a Encoder.Builder for constructing RandomDistributedScalarEncoders.

    The base class architecture is put together in such a way where boilerplate initialization can be kept to a minimum for implementing subclasses, while avoiding the mistake-proneness of extremely long argument lists.

    Author:
    Anubhav Chaturvedi
